Functional Requirements:

  1. Administrator Access
  2. Sign up details for various users
  3. Search donor by locality or blood group
  4. Donor points
  5. Checking eligibility of the donor
  6. Notification pannel
  7. Connecting with social networking websites
  8. Messages/E-mail functionality
  
Non-Functional Requirements:

  1. Searching multiple donors
  2. Notification via both E-mail and text messages
